This layer provides security related layers.

meta-accounts
=============
This layer provides builtin user in AliOS.

meta-apparmor
=============
This layer provides apparmor, a Mandatory Access Control(MAC) implementation based on LSM in linux kernel.

meta-secure-base
===============
This layer provides base and common recipes for security layers.

meta-secure-core
===============
This layer provides ima, luks, tpm1.x, tpm2.0 security features.


For details, please read the README in each layer.
